I've been keeping you apart.

1260
01:46:49,899 --> 01:46:53,100
When we met two years ago,
I was in love with someone else.

1261
01:46:53,180 --> 01:46:56,180
And she just came back
into my life.

1262
01:46:56,939 --> 01:46:59,500
She broke my heart...
and I'm sorry!

1263
01:47:00,100 --> 01:47:01,420
Oh, my God.

1264
01:47:07,260 --> 01:47:10,100
l... Rebecca, I know...

1265
01:47:10,180 --> 01:47:12,020
I know that I'm still in love with her.

1266
01:47:12,819 --> 01:47:14,819
I just... I needed you to know.

1267
01:47:15,619 --> 01:47:16,939
Knowwhat?

1268
01:47:18,100 --> 01:47:20,100
Know what, Matthew?

1269
01:47:21,379 --> 01:47:23,420
That I'm not the girl
that can break your heart?

